        <mxCell id="ShZeyjhVx2JSlpE_-DkV-2" value="(a) Write the graph above as an adjacency matrix, then as an adjacency list. What&lt;br&gt;would be different if the graph were undirected instead?&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
